T02TD2314E:257b-51: gtsug lag khang chen gnas brtan pa //
T02TD2314E:258a-2: gnas ma bu yi sde pa ni //
T02TD2314E:258a-3: kun gyis bkur ba rnam pa gsum //
T02TD2314E:258a-4: yul don slob dpon bye brag gi / tha dad rnam pa bco brgyad do //
T02TD2314E:258a-5: rang rgyal byang chub don gnyer bas //
T02TD2314E:258a-6: gzung ba'i rtog pa spangs phyir dang //
T02TD2314E:258a-7: 'dzin pa ma spangs phyir na ste//
T02TD2314E:258a-8: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
T02TD2314E:258a-9: bskal ba brgya yi mthar thug par //
T02TD2314E:258a-10: bsgoms pas byang chub reg par 'gyur //
T02TD2314E:258a-12: yan lag bcu gnyis chags gsum mo //
T02TD2314E:258a-13: sngon dang phyi mthar gnyis gnyis dang //
T02TD2314E:258a-14: bar du brgyad yongs rdzogs ldan la //
T02TD2314E:258a-15: ma rig nyon mongs sngon gnas skabs //
T02TD2314E:258a-17: rnam shes mtshams sbyor phung po yin //
T02TD2314E:258a-18: ming dang gzugs ni de phan chad //
T02TD2314E:258a-19: skye mched drug dod tshun chad do //
T02TD2314E:258a-20: de ni gsum 'dus tshun chad do //
T02TD2314E:258a-21: reg pa bde sdug la sogs kyi //
T02TD2314E:258a-22: rgyu shes nus pa tshun chad do//
T02TD2314E:258a-23: chor 'khrig tshun chad sred pa ni //
T02TD2314E:258a-24: longs spyod 'khrig pa chags bcas kyi //
T02TD2314E:258a-25: nye bar len pa longs spyod rnams //
T02TD2314E:258a-26: thob par bya phyir yongs rgyug pa'o //
T02TD2314E:258a-28: las de nyid ni srid pa yin //
T02TD2314E:258a-29: nying mtshams sbyor ba skye ba yin //
T02TD2314E:258a-30: tshor ba'i bar ni rga shi yin //
T02TD2314E:258a-32: gtso bo'i phyir na yan lag bsgrags //
T02TD2314E:258a-33: sngon dang phyi mtha' bar dag la //
T02TD2314E:258a-34: rmongs pa rnam par bzlog phyir ro //
T02TD2314E:258a-35: nyon mongs gsum mo las gnyis so //
T02TD2314E:258a-36: bzhi bdun de bzhin 'bras bu yin //
T02TD2314E:258a-37: gnyis kyi rgyu 'bras mdor bsdus pa ;
T02TD2314E:258a-38: / bar ma'i rjes su dpag pa las //
T02TD2314E:258a-41: yan lag bcu gnyis de dag las //
T02TD2314E:258a-42: rgyu ni rnam lnga 'bras bu bdun //
T02TD2314E:258a-44: mngon par 'grub byed grub pa dang //
T02TD2314E:258a-45: nyes dmigs kyi ni yan lag ste //
T02TD2314E:258a-46: gsum bzhi gsum gyi gcig rim pa bzhin //
T02TD2314E:258a-48: sdug bsngal nyid ni rim bzhin du //
T02TD2314E:258a-49: ldang dang bzhi dang lnga yin no //
T02TD2314E:258a-50: khams gsum na ni rim bzhin du //
T02TD2314E:258b-0: bcu gnyis bcu gcig bcu yis 'jug / rdzus skyes yan @258b lag bcu gcig gis //
T02TD2314E:258b-1: mngal dang sgong skyes bcu gnyis kyis //
T02TD2314E:258b-2: drod gsher las skyes ci rigs 'jug / de bzhin 'gro ba lnga la sbyar //
T02TD2314E:258b-3: gsum po dag las gnyis 'byung ste //
T02TD2314E:258b-4: gnyis las bdun 'byung bdun las kyang //
T02TD2314E:258b-6: nyid ni yid dang yid du 'khor //
T02TD2314E:258b-7: 'khor ba'i ngo bo rnam pa dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-8: gang gzhig gang du gang gis ngang //
T02TD2314E:258b-9: ji ltar ji srid nyes dmigs ni //
T02TD2314E:258b-10: mtha' yas tshogs kyis rab tu 'jug / brtsam par bya zhing 'byung bar bya //
T02TD2314E:258b-11: sangs rgyas bstan la 'jug par bya //
T02TD2314E:258b-12: 'dam bu'i khyim na glang chen bzhin //
T02TD2314E:258b-13: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par bya //
T02TD2314E:258b-14: gang zhig rab tu bag yod par //
T02TD2314E:258b-16: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
T02TD2314E:258b-17: sdug bsngal tha mar byed par 'gyur //
T02TD2314E:258b-18: mya ngan gang las 'da' ba dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-19: gang zhig gang gis gang gi tshe //
T02TD2314E:258b-20: gang gis gang phyir ji lta bur //
T02TD2314E:258b-21: ji srid ngo bo rnam pa dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-22: thob bya dbye ba phrin las dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-23: yon tan tshogs kyis ldog pa'o //
T02TD2314E:258b-24: mu stegs pa ni rnam pa gnyis //
T02TD2314E:258b-25: sprul pa ba dang rang rgyud pa //
T02TD2314E:258b-26: de yang skyes thob sbyor 'byung ngo //
T02TD2314E:258b-27: skyes thob rigs chad log sred can //
T02TD2314E:258b-28: sbyor byung bsam gtan rtog ge ba //
T02TD2314E:258b-29: bsam gtan pa ni mngon shes mthus //
T02TD2314E:258b-30: lta ba drug cu gnyis su rtogs //
T02TD2314E:258b-31: rtag par smra ba rnam bzhi dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-32: kha cig rtag par smra ba bzhi //
T02TD2314E:258b-33: mtha' yod sogs bzhi mi spong bzhi //
T02TD2314E:258b-34: rgyud med gnyis ni sngon mthar rtog /'du shes yod smra bcu drug dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-35: med smra brgyad dang de bzhin du //
T02TD2314E:258b-36: yod min med min smra ba brgyad //
T02TD2314E:258b-37: chad smra bdun dang tshe 'di la //
T02TD2314E:258b-38: mya ngan 'da' bar smra ba lnga //
T02TD2314E:258b-39: phyi ma'i mthar rtog lta ba'o //
T02TD2314E:258b-40: rtog ge ba ni grangs can sogs //
T02TD2314E:258b-42: grangs can yon tan gsum du brjod //
T02TD2314E:258b-43: snying stobs rdul dang mun pa'o //
T02TD2314E:258b-44: rangs dang mgu dang kun dga' dang //
T02TD2314E:258b-45: bde bzhi pa yi sems nyi dag / res 'ga' yang ni snang gyur pa //
T02TD2314E:258b-46: de dag snying stobs yon tan no //
T02TD2314E:258b-47: mi dga' ba dang yongs gdud dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-1: dag / gang du snang ba'i gtan tshigs kyis //
T02TD2314E:259a-2: de dag rdul gyi rtags su 'dod //
T02TD2314E:259a-3: rmongs pa de bzhin gti mug dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-4: bag med gnyid dang gsal ba dang /
T02TD2314E:259a-5: len 'ga' yang ni snang gyur pa //
T02TD2314E:259a-6: de dag mun pa'i yon tan no //
T02TD2314E:259a-7: yon tan gsum gyi rang bzhin /
T02TD2314E:259a-8: mchog / mthong ba'i lam du 'gyur ma yin //
T02TD2314E:259a-9: mthong ba'i lam du gang gyur pa / sgyu ma bzhin du shin tu gsog / rang bzhin las ni chen po ste //
T02TD2314E:259a-10: de las nga rgyal rnam gsum 'byung //
T02TD2314E:259a-11: da la dbang po bcu gcig dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-12: de tsam lnga'o de lnga las //
T02TD2314E:259a-13: 'byung ba lnga ste nyi shu bzhi//
T02TD2314E:259a-14: gco bo nyid dang rnam 'gyur ro //
T02TD2314E:259a-15: de dag sems pa yod ma yin //
T02TD2314E:259a-16: skyes bu kun rig sems pa can //
T02TD2314E:259a-17: de dag nyi shu lngas shes na //
T02TD2314E:259a-18: ral ba spyi bo gtsug phud kyis //
T02TD2314E:259a-19: bsti gnas gang du dga' ba der //
T02TD2314E:259a-21: byer bag pa ni don drug 'dod //
T02TD2314E:259a-22: rdzas dang yon tan las dang spyi //
T02TD2314E:259a-23: bye brag 'du ba rnams pa drug / rdzas dgu yon tan nyi shu bzhi //
T02TD2314E:259a-24: las lnga spyi gnyis bye brag gnyis //
T02TD2314E:259a-25: de bzhin 'du ba'ang rnam gnyis te //
T02TD2314E:259a-26: de nyid du gshes rig pa'i mchog //
T02TD2314E:259a-27: rig byed kun gyi pha rol phyin //
T02TD2314E:259a-28: gcer bu ba rnams don dgu smra //
T02TD2314E:259a-29: srog dang zag pa sdom pa dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-30: nges par dga' dang 'chi ba dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-31: las dang sdig dang bsod nams dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-32: thar pa zhes bya don dgu po //
T02TD2314E:259a-33: gang gis mthong ste rnam par dag / rigs ba can don bcu drug 'dod //
T02TD2314E:259a-34: tshad ma gzhal bya the tshom dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-35: dgos pa dpe dang grub mtha' dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-36: cha shas rtog ge gtan la dbab //
T02TD2314E:259a-37: rtsod dang brjod dang rgol ba dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-38: rgyu ltar snang ba tshig dor dang //
T02TD2314E:259a-39: ltag chod chad pa'i gnas rnams te //
T02TD2314E:259a-40: bcu drug gis ni nges par 'byung //
T02TD2314E:259a-41: dpyod pa pa ni don bzhir brjod //
T02TD2314E:259a-42: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung //
T02TD2314E:259a-43: de dag 'dus ma byas pa ste //
T02TD2314E:259a-44: rtag tu skye 'gag med par gnas //
T02TD2314E:259a-45: de bas las 'bras yod ma yin //
T02TD2314E:259a-46: sngon dang phyi mtha' de bzhin med //
T02TD2314E:259a-47: gang zhig de ltar rnam dpyod pa //
T02TD2314E:259a-48: mthong pa tsam gyis rnam grol 'gyur //
T02TD2314E:259a-49: khyab 'jug byed rgyur rma ba rnams //
T02TD2314E:259b-0: nyi ma'i nang na khyab bdag 'jug / skar nang 'od gnas zla ba @259b yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-1: rlung nang nga ni 'od zer can //
T02TD2314E:259b-2: snang ba can na nyi ma yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-3: rig bye dang na snyan tshig dang //
T02TD2314E:259b-4: lha nang nga ni brgya byin te //
T02TD2314E:259b-5: dbang po'i nang na yid yin no //
T02TD2314E:259b-6: 'byung ba'i nang na sa yin zhing //
T02TD2314E:259b-7: nga ni bde byed drag po'ang yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-8: srin po gnod spyin nang rol bdag / nor lha'i nang na me lha pa //
T02TD2314E:259b-9: ri bo'i nang na nga ri rab //
T02TD2314E:259b-10: nga ni yi ge'i nang na aa //
T02TD2314E:259b-11: nya dang rus sbal phag dang ni //
T02TD2314E:259b-12: mi yi seng ge mi thung dang //
T02TD2314E:259b-13: dga' byed ra ma na nag po //
T02TD2314E:259b-14: sangs rgyas tsar ti ka dang bcu //
T02TD2314E:259b-15: gang gis khyab 'jug yon tan rnams //
T02TD2314E:259b-16: rtag tu bsgoms na bde thob 'gyur //
T02TD2314E:259b-17: dbang phyug byed rgyur 'dod pa rnams //
T02TD2314E:259b-19: byed pa po ni dbang phyug yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-20: de ni yon tan brgya dang ldan //
T02TD2314E:259b-21: rab phra yang ba mchod par 'os //
T02TD2314E:259b-22: bdag por gyur dang dbang du gyur //
T02TD2314E:259b-23: gar yang phyin dang 'dod dgur ldan //
T02TD2314E:259b-24: de bzhin dga' mgur gnas pa'o //
T02TD2314E:259b-25: lag pa dag dang rkang pa dang //
T02TD2314E:259b-26: mig dang gdong dang lus rnams kyi //
T02TD2314E:259b-27: mang po bskyed cing 'jig byed pas //
T02TD2314E:259b-28: des na phra bar brjod pa yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-29: mkha' dang rlung dang sa dang ni //
T02TD2314E:259b-30: chu dang me dag gnas byed cing //
T02TD2314E:259b-31: sdud pa dang ni rgyas byed pas //
T02TD2314E:259b-32: nges na yang par brjod pa yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-33: 'jig rten gsum na mchod gyur cing //
T02TD2314E:259b-34: gnas pa bdag dang rgyu ba dang //
T02TD2314E:259b-35: 'byung po kun gyis brjed pas na //
T02TD2314E:259b-36: des ni mchod par 'os pa yin //
T02TD2314E:259b-37: 'byung po kun la dbang byed cing //
T02TD2314E:259b-38: gnas pa bdag dang rgyu ba dang //
T02TD2314E:259b-39: gang dang gang 'dod de byed pas //
T02TD2314E:259b-40: des na bdag por gyur zhes bya //
T02TD2314E:259b-41: bdag la rag las rang dbang can //
T02TD2314E:259b-43: thams cad dbang du gyur zhes bya //
T02TD2314E:259b-44: mtho ris ngan song kun khyab pas //
T02TD2314E:259b-45: des na gar yang phyin zhes bya //
T02TD2314E:259b-46: snying stobs rdul dang mun pa gsum //
T02TD2314E:259b-47: de dag gang la gnas gyur pa //
T02TD2314E:259b-48: mig 'byed tsam gyis byed gyur pas //
T02TD2314E:259b-49: des na 'dod dgur ldan zhes bya //
T02TD2314E:259b-50: thar pa'ang yang na lha yi lus //
T02TD2314E:259b-51: gang du dag nyid 'dod pa dag / thams cad 'dod pas thob gyur pas / des na dga' mgur gnas zhes bya //
T02TD2314E:260a-1: pu skyes nas 'dug / de yi 'di kun skyes shing 'jig par byed //
T02TD2314E:260a-2: de ni dbang dag mchog sbyin lha mchog bya //
T02TD2314E:260a-3: yon tan byed po shin tu zhi ba thob //
T02TD2314E:260a-4: skyes pa po 'di shes pa yod min te //
T02TD2314E:260a-5: bdag gi bde sdug bdag la rang dbang med //
T02TD2314E:260a-6: dbang phyug gis btang yang na mtho ris sam //
T02TD2314E:260a-7: g-yang sa dag tu 'gro ba kho nar 'gyur //
T02TD2314E:260a-8: dbang phyugs rdza mkhan lta bur sna tshogs 'di sbrul byed por ma gyur na //
T02TD2314E:260a-9: ri rab 'di mi grub cing sa gzhi 'di min rgya mtsho 'ang ma yin te //
T02TD2314E:260a-10: nyi zla skar ldan 'di ltar bkod pa 'di dag mig yul du med 'gyur //
T02TD2314E:260a-11: yod pa'i phyir ni dbang phyug 'gro ba'i byed po yin zhes 'ga' zhig smra //
T02TD2314E:260a-12: phra zhing bsam gyis mi khyab rab srab byed pa kun rig kun byed pa //
T02TD2314E:260a-13: rnal 'byor goms pas thob pa blo can bsam gtan pa yi bsam gtan yul //
T02TD2314E:260a-14: nyi ma zla bas chu me rlung phyogs dang nam mkha'i lus can te //
T02TD2314E:260a-15: zhi ba'i bde dga' 'dod pa rnams kyis dbang phyug rtag tu bsgoms //
T02TD2314E:260a-16: dus la ltos par smra ba rnams //
T02TD2314E:260a-17: dngos kun dus kyis bsgyur ba ste //
T02TD2314E:260a-18: gang gi zhang po nor lha dang //
T02TD2314E:260a-19: gang pha nor rgyas yin pa yi //
T02TD2314E:260a-20: 'jigs med khro bo 'ang bsad gyur pas //
T02TD2314E:260a-21: dus ni 'da' bar dka' ba yin //
T02TD2314E:260a-23: skye dgu rnams sdud dus kyis byed //
T02TD2314E:260a-24: dus kyi gnyid log sad par byed //
T02TD2314E:260a-25: dus ni 'da' bar dka' ba yin //
T02TD2314E:260a-26: srung ba sum brtsegs 'obs ni rgya mtsho dang //
T02TD2314E:260a-27: dmag mi srin po nor ni nor spyin sbyor //
T02TD2314E:260a-28: gang zhig bstan bcos pa sangs tshad mnyam ba'i //
T02TD2314E:260a-29: sgra sgrogs bu de'ang dus kyi dbang gis nyams //
T02TD2314E:260a-30: ngo bo nyid rgyur smra ba ni //
T02TD2314E:260a-31: dngos rnams ngo bo nyid kyis 'grub //
T02TD2314E:260a-32: me yi dmar ba nyid dang ni //
T02TD2314E:260a-33: dam pa gzhan don byed nyid dang //
T02TD2314E:260a-34: dam pa min pa'i brtse med nyid //
T02TD2314E:260a-35: gsum po ngo bo nyid kyis grub //
T02TD2314E:260a-36: tsher ma rnor bar gyur pa su yis byas //
T02TD2314E:260a-37: ri dags bya yi ri mo su yis byas //
T02TD2314E:260a-38: bu ram shing mngar ni ma pa kha ba dag /'di dag thams cad ngo bo nyid kyis grub //
T02TD2314E:260a-39: nyi mtshan zhing zla ba rab bsil dang //
T02TD2314E:260a-40: skye bo chags shing thub pa de min la //
T02TD2314E:260a-41: bde bar bsil sdug bsngal rab gdung ba //
T02TD2314E:260b-0: drug po 'di dag @260b ngo bo nyid kyis grub //
T02TD2314E:260b-1: gang dag rgyu med smra ba ni //
T02TD2314E:260b-2: thams cad rgyu la ltos med par //
T02TD2314E:260b-3: dngos po rnams kyis skye ba ste //
T02TD2314E:260b-4: nyi ma padma'i ge sar sogs //
T02TD2314E:260b-5: sna tshogs gang gis byas pa yin //
T02TD2314E:260b-6: rma bya'i mdongs la sogs pa yang //
T02TD2314E:260b-7: sna tshogs gang gis sprul pa yin //
T02TD2314E:260b-8: ji ltar char rlung la sogs pa //
T02TD2314E:260b-9: glo bur 'byung phyir rgyu med ltar //
T02TD2314E:260b-10: sdug bsngal la sogs rgyu med nyid //
T02TD2314E:260b-11: shin tu rgya chen rab zab la //
T02TD2314E:260b-12: sgyid lug shin tu ma sbyangs la //
T02TD2314E:260b-13: bdag bzhin sgra dag gti mug gis //
T02TD2314E:260b-14: dag ltar theg pa che la smod //
T02TD2314E:260b-15: tshul khrims las ni nyams bla yi //
T02TD2314E:260b-16: lta las cis kyang ma yin te //
T02TD2314E:260b-17: tshul khrims kyis ni mtho ris 'gro //
T02TD2314E:260b-19: gti mug dbang gis bsgrigs gyur te //
T02TD2314E:260b-20: gang zhig yang dag gegs byed pa //
T02TD2314E:260b-21: de la dge ba'i 'gro ba'ang med //
T02TD2314E:260b-22: thar pa med par smos ci dgos //
T02TD2314E:260b-23: gnod pa'i sa bon gyur pa yi//
T02TD2314E:260b-24: mu stegs byed mang mthong nas ni //
T02TD2314E:260b-26: snying rjer mi 'gyur su zhig yod //
T02TD2314E:260b-27: de phyir thar pa don gnyer rnams //
T02TD2314E:260b-28: chos kyi dbyings su lta bar gyis //
T02TD2314E:260b-29: chos kyi dbyings su lta ba'i glu //
T02TD2314E:260b-30: slob dpon chen po 'di pam ka ras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2314E:260b-32: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po de nyid dang //
T02TD2314E:260b-33: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dge slong tshul khrims rgyal bas bsgyur ba'o//
